Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Itoshi no Kotodama
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In my dreams, I will embrace,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.17,0:00:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}anata e no omoi dake o
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just my feelings for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}yume ni dakishimete
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very slowly, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.93,0:00:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}yukkuri to watashi wa ima
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I am starting to take an adult form.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ah otona no kakera ni kawaru
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.15,0:00:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The love I hold in my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.15,0:00:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}yume ni aru aiji dake ni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,shines brighter than anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.91,0:00:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}nani yori mo kagayaite
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}oh kui ga nai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.38,0:01:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I was able to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.38,0:01:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}mata anata ni deaete watashi wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I was happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.53,0:01:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}shiawase datta yo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 1:\NSublimation
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.51,0:01:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Akio Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.35,0:01:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'm so tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We don't know what caused your illness"?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Are you sure you're not tired\Njust because it's summer?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.86,0:01:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. It's not like I'm proud that I've been\Nsick ever since the start of summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.57,0:02:01.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not gonna make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.45,0:02:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish the doctors would just do their job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.79,0:02:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow. Hey, where do you think you're looking?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why you're in such a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.76,0:02:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But lately I've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.52,0:02:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What? I get the feeling I saw something weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it's just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! My charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.78,0:02:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When did I drop that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:38.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.95,0:02:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.54,0:02:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You like me, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.71,0:02:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.70,0:03:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry. Do it quick. Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.70,0:03:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm losing my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.79,0:03:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:03:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Urn, listen, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I feel like I should introduce myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just because you knocked me over,\Nyou think you can be my friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.41,0:04:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you staring at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do that. Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.41,0:04:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, well, no reason. Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me everything that\Njust happened was a dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, treat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.01,0:05:07.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To a marshmallow and fruit parfait at Todai Cafe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.82,0:05:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.53,0:05:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, hut I wonder what I saw back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.95,0:05:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why have you been doing nothing\Nbut stare at me all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.46,0:05:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, ha ha ha! I'm Koga Shigemaro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.96,0:05:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tachibana Aki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.42,0:05:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait don't tell me you ran into me on\Npurpose just so you could ask me out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it at all! I really was in a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell am I doing here!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.40,0:06:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap. I won't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.77,0:06:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was supposed to give this to my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.32,0:06:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going overseas,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.49,0:06:13.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my grandfather asked me to\Ngive him this good luck charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.66,0:06:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:20.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. My body...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.58,0:06:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My body does things I can't control. It happens a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.13,0:06:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you missed your chance to give him the charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.47,0:06:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.30,0:06:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you could always just mail it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:35.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. I guess I could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.71,0:07:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Yoshihira, it's just you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:10.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're that jumpy, you must be\Nhiding something nasty from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hide it, don't hide it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.23,0:07:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this summer vacation's gonna be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Introduce me to your pretty girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one from Todai Cafe! Todai Cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.70,0:07:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were on a date with her there, last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.83,0:07:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you guys from the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.20,0:07:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She saw something really weird too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Saw something weird?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:48.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.63,0:07:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yesterday, I must not have really been myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.09,0:07:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. "Weird" doesn't even begin to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.81,0:08:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that girl from...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.31,0:08:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nice to meet you. I'm, um, Fujishima Yoshihira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.77,0:08:12.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You yelled, "Ah! Watch out!" out of nowhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.20,0:08:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then suddenly jumped off the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.36,0:08:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shop owners and the other\Ncustomers started yelling,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dine and dash!" and "He killed himself\Nfor revenge on his girlfriend!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.50,0:08:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then, "You need to pay his bill."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You abandoned this pretty girl? You ungrateful ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.71,0:08:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But back then, I could've sworn\NI saw a girl fall off the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I thought I saw the cliff start to erode back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.05,0:09:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I don't see any debris.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.47,0:09:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder where she went?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if he was trying to kill himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.72,0:09:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's gotta he it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.73,0:09:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He was killing himself to make the\Ngirl who dumped him feel guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I bet he was just dining 'n' dashing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.61,0:09:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shigemaro, I totally saw that too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.16,0:09:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost. A {\i1}ghost{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.99,0:09:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That place has always been a\Nreally famous spot for ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.66,0:09:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister told me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghosts like areas with a lot of water. Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.25,0:09:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that. Pay me what you owe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:55.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Bill for food and property damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.80,0:09:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's really that expensive?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pay! I'll pay already, jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you your change later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Bye then!\N– You see, ever since I was little, I've been extra sensitive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.22,0:10:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– You see, ever since I was little, I've been extra sensitive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– I've got it! I think I'll have anoter\Nmarshmallow and fruit parfait.\N– You see, ever since I was little, I've been extra sensitive...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.56,0:10:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– I've got it! I think I'll have anoter\Nmarshmallow and fruit parfait.\N– ...to ghosts and auras and that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.40,0:10:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to ghosts and auras and that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.69,0:10:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, I'm gonna pig out man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.98,0:10:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lowest-level ghost is what we call hyo-grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.19,0:10:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then if she possesses a human,\Nshe graduates to Jiba-grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but she's bound to the land she's on and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.24,0:10:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you leaving? H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.62,0:10:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take ya home, babe! Um, I mean, miss!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.13,0:10:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So you saw her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! My back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for trying to show\Noff like that at your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I didn't end up giving this to Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.65,0:10:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, it's probably best that you keep it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must give you more things that you'll need.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.91,0:11:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we in such a creepy place?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.50,0:11:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want someone to see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:16.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.46,0:11:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it. You mean your rival reporter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.63,0:11:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want her to beat you to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.68,0:11:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this becomes a big scoop,\Ngive me the reward you promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.85,0:11:29.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have my word. Just be a good guide for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this path sure goes on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like the perfect atmosphere for ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.78,0:11:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot. I wasn't talking about a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.03,0:11:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn out your light.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.91,0:11:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure is quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:11.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a charm we've kept in our family\Nfor years to protect against wild spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've come into contact with one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That must mean she sees something in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.40,0:12:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that girl is dead. She was really pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.74,0:12:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In that case, you must communicate with\Nher and help her pass on to the next life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.66,0:12:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She has chosen you for that purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.67,0:12:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Shigemaro...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.92,0:12:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.55,0:12:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like it'll come any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.34,0:12:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut that out, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.39,0:12:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.23,0:12:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.36,0:13:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.03,0:13:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.33,0:13:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time anyone has told me I'm pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People who see me are always frightened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.09,0:13:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They think I'm here to hurt them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.88,0:13:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shes in human form!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.51,0:13:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if she'll show up on film?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.55,0:13:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit. Yoshihira, get me another camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.52,0:13:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This makes me ashamed to be your sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.40,0:13:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's follow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.23,0:13:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.74,0:13:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.87,0:13:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where she went?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute. Something's shining.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.75,0:13:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should we check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.68,0:14:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was this ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:16.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It happened a very long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.79,0:15:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He tried to save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.25,0:16:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm still bitter about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to be able to thank him, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.96,0:16:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell him how I feel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.97,0:16:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know his name or any way of finding him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.10,0:16:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He carved a wooden statue in memory of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.98,0:16:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, an evil spider-spirit that\Nsteals people's feelings took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A spider-spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.15,0:16:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.74,0:16:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aki-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.95,0:16:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go help her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.13,0:16:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hige-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.05,0:16:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.05,0:16:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.97,0:17:00.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait right there! I'll come save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.98,0:17:10.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away... from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.73,0:17:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did this happen to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.70,0:17:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.79,0:17:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run for it! You're up against a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.42,0:17:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't just leave you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What kind of monster is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.18,0:17:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... the spider-spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shigemaro-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lay off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.66,0:18:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.08,0:18:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These exorcism papers Grandpa gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.34,0:18:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin pyo to sha kai jin retsu zai zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:29.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.69,0:18:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.02,0:18:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something written on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.61,0:18:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rest in peace. –Shinohara Tatsuya"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.28,0:18:39.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was the fight fun for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.16,0:18:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like a monster... a demon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.04,0:18:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's that charm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa there, go easy on me, pal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.54,0:18:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't done nothing bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just possessing that chick over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's probably more correct to say\Nshe forced me to possess her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forced you to possess her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.30,0:19:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the kind of body she has.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.85,0:19:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A ghost-attracting body?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.23,0:19:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not exactly a talent, but I guess it kinda is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better release me soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.07,0:19:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.99,0:19:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, most normal humans don't\Nremember anything about ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:29.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That chick over there won't even\Nremember our spider friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you defeated him, you broke his magical field.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.46,0:19:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So then, what am I still doing here? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want an explanation from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.01,0:19:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she and I are just–
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.05,0:19:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was attracted to you
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because she knew, subconsciously, that\Nyou could liberate me from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.69,0:19:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone with your gift would have worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.19,0:19:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Anyone"?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.66,0:20:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, he's such a softie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.33,0:20:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I'd better get myself exorcised\Nbefore that chick wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? What were you daydreaming about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you catch a cold or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.69,0:20:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.19,0:20:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sis has been out cold, sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.20,0:20:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.28,0:20:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.37,0:20:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like this summer vacation's gonna be fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.45,0:20:52.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Introduce me to your pretty girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one from Todai Cafe! Todai Cafe.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.17,0:21:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were on a date with her there, last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.38,0:21:04.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you guys from the bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.09,0:21:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said the exact same thing yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.64,0:21:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? "Yesterday"? How's that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.76,0:21:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yesterday I must not have really been myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.44,0:21:18.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup. "Weird" doesn't even begin to describe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're that girl from...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.49,0:21:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nice to meet you. I'm, um, Fujishima Yoshihira.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You yelled, "Ah! Watch out!" out of nowhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.25,0:21:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then suddenly jumped off the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:38.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.33,0:21:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The shop owners and the other\Ncustomers started yelling,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.46,0:21:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dine and dash!" and "He killed himself\Nfor revenge on his girlfriend!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:45.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then, "You need to pay his bill".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.42,0:21:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.55,0:21:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You abandoned this pretty girl? You ungrateful ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:55.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is like deja vu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:22:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike you, most normal humans don't\Nremember anything about ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.57,0:22:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that Pay me what you owe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.07,0:22:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.49,0:22:15.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.50,0:22:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.75,0:22:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rest in peace. –Shinohara Tatsuya"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.67,0:22:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinohara Tatsuya"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.67,0:22:24.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the name of the Chief of Medicine\Nat the hospital I go to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.46,0:22:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's some random knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not random. He's my personal physician!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.05,0:22:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sick? You don't look it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.43,0:22:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always had a weak constitution.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.06,0:22:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But yesterday, by Todai Cafe I–
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.39,0:22:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! My money!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.94,0:22:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shigemaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.05,0:23:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Chief of Medicine: Shinohara Tatsua| Akio Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.50,0:23:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so? He became the Chief of Medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.63,0:23:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.97,0:23:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that wooden carving was made in my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.68,0:24:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the feelings he poured into the carving\Nwere stolen by the spider-spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.81,0:24:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I returned it to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.40,0:24:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't changed a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.03,0:24:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go stand by him?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.66,0:25:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.36,0:25:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.65,0:25:34.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this, I can at least rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.36,0:25:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I regret leaving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.95,0:25:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.63,0:25:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.05,0:25:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.92,0:25:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so warm.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.20,0:26:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.54,0:27:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not down there. No, I'm shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.22,0:27:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give me yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.89,0:27:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're very pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.35,0:27:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.58,0:27:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.25,0:27:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cumming.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.83,0:27:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cumming! I'm cumming!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.42,0:27:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.93,0:28:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cumming!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.69,0:28:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.62,0:28:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.11,0:29:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Chapter 2:\NReturn
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.15,0:29:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.50,0:30:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The instant I open my eyes,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.50,0:30:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}me o aketa shunkan ni
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.72,0:30:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My happiness flees from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.72,0:30:13.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}shiawase wa nigeteku kara
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.31,0:30:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I want to stay this way forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.31,0:30:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}eien ni kono mama de
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.69,0:30:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With my eyes closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.69,0:30:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}me o tojite itai
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.74,0:30:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I am in your arms,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.74,0:30:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}ima anata no ude no naka ni
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.08,0:30:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Embraced gently,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.08,0:30:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}yasashiku dakarete
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.79,0:30:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I am changing into an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.79,0:30:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}sou watashi wa maboroshi ni kawaru keredo
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.64,0:30:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't let it fade away,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.64,0:30:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}douka kesanai de
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.10,0:31:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The love that remains in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.10,0:31:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}mune ni tomaru ai o
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.52,0:31:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surely, someday in the future,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.52,0:31:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}kitto mirai demo
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.45,0:31:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, and only I, will be yours forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.45,0:31:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}watashi dake ga your forever